descript.abstract: Eastern Bering Sea NMFS crab-groundfish survey station grid including Pribilof Islands and St. Matthew Island grid corner stations.
descript.purpose: Data set was developed to depict, as polygons, the 20 x 20 nautical mile station grid used for the eastern Bering Sea NMFS crab-groundfish bottom trawl survey. Polygon coverage with alpha-numeric station identifiers is used to assign station id's to haul data (point coverages).
